Water Logging App
	- An app that helps you track your daily water intake.
	
Primary features
	- Users are able to set a goal for their daily in-take (Ex: 64 oz).
	- Users are able to set reminders for drinking water throughout the day.
	- Users can log specific increments of water (8oz, 10oz, 12oz, 16oz, etc).
	- Users are able to see their water in-take history.
    	- Info is updated to Health app if user gives permission.

Secondary features
	- Users will be able to see a progress bar for their daily water in-take.
